Class ProductTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • tree.GenericTree<IProduct>
      • tree.ProductTree
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDeepCopy, ITree<IProduct>, ISearchableByFilter<ITreeNode<IProduct>>

    public class ProductTree
extends GenericTree<IProduct>
    This class represents a ITree of IProducts. It extends the GenericTree and binds its typeparameter TREETYPE to IProduct. This means that there are only ITreeNodes of IProducts in the ProductTree.
